---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="For Agencies">
    <main>
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>For Agencies: Pioneer the Future of Legacy Representation</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Unlock unprecedented revenue streams through digital estate management and posthumous talent representation</p>
        </div>

        <section class="content">
            <div class="info-card vision">
                <h2>The Agency Opportunity</h2>
                <p>"Living with the Ghost of Sam" represents more than just another productionâ€”it's the vanguard of an emerging market for talent agencies willing to innovate. As digital recreation technology advances, agencies that establish themselves as leaders in posthumous representation will secure a competitive advantage in a growing sector that bridges entertainment history with cutting-edge technology.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card estate-relationships">
                <h2>Building the Estate Representation Division</h2>
                <p>This series provides the perfect foundation for agencies to develop a specialized estate management division:</p>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h3>Estate Acquisition Strategy</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Leverage the series as a showcase for respectful, authentic digital recreation</li>
                        <li>Demonstrate clear revenue pathways for previously unmonetized legacy content</li>
                        <li>Present estate managers with concrete examples of positive legacy enhancement</li>
                        <li>Offer comprehensive rights management across emerging technologies</li>
                        <li>Position your agency as the authoritative voice in posthumous representation</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card revenue">
                <h2>Multi-Stream Revenue Model</h2>
                <div class="two-column">
                    <div>
                        <h3>Immediate Revenue Opportunities:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Performance licensing fees for digital recreations</li>
                            <li>Rights management for classic material integration</li>
                            <li>Merchandising opportunities through renewed interest</li>
                            <li>Documentary and supplemental content development</li>
                            <li>Archival footage licensing and enhancement</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3>Long-Term Value Creation:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Establishment of ongoing digital performance rights</li>
                            <li>Creation of new IP derived from legacy personalities</li>
                            <li>Development of cross-platform legacy presence</li>
                            <li>Educational and institutional licensing programs</li>
                            <li>Revival touring and live event opportunities</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card synergy">
                <h2>Synergy with Current Talent Representation</h2>
                <p>Estate representation creates powerful advantages for your living talent roster:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Unique opportunities for current clients to perform alongside legendary figures</li>
                    <li>Establishment of future legacy management for today's performers</li>
                    <li>Cross-promotion between contemporary and historical talent</li>
                    <li>Educational and mentorship programs leveraging preserved performances</li>
                    <li>Enhanced agency prestige through association with iconic entertainment legacies</li>
                    <li>Expanded negotiating leverage with producers seeking both current and legacy talent</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card legal-framework">
                <h2>Pioneering the Legal Framework</h2>
                <p>Agencies that establish themselves in this space now will help shape industry standards:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Develop boilerplate contracts for digital recreation rights</li>
                    <li>Establish standard compensation models for technological performances</li>
                    <li>Create protocols for quality control and approval processes</li>
                    <li>Define boundaries for acceptable use and artistic interpretation</li>
                    <li>Build relationships with technology partners for ongoing development</li>
                    <li>Secure favorable terms before market standardization</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card estates">
                <h2>Priority Comedy Estates</h2>
                <p>Based on our development process, these estates represent particularly valuable partnership opportunities:</p>
                <div class="estate-grid">
                    <div class="estate-card">
                        <h3>The Sam Kinison Estate</h3>
                        <p>Central to our series concept with significant unrealized legacy potential and passionate fan base spanning multiple generations.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="estate-card">
                        <h3>The John Belushi Estate</h3>
                        <p>Iconic physical comedy perfectly suited for digital recreation with substantial unreleased material and cross-media potential.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="estate-card">
                        <h3>The Gilda Radner Estate</h3>
                        <p>Groundbreaking female comedian with enduring cultural relevance and strong potential for contemporary reintroduction.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="estate-card">
                        <h3>The Chris Farley Estate</h3>
                        <p>Beloved physical comedian with significant unrealized potential and strong nostalgic appeal across demographics.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card competitive">
                <h2>Competitive Advantage</h2>
                <p>The agency that establishes itself as the leader in this space will:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Secure first-mover advantage in an emerging high-value representation category</li>
                    <li>Build institutional knowledge and systems before competitors enter the space</li>
                    <li>Develop valuable relationships with key technology partners</li>
                    <li>Establish market-standard contract language and deal structures</li>
                    <li>Position itself as the natural home for future estate clients</li>
                    <li>Create a valuable new division with diversified revenue streams</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card case-study">
                <h2>Estate Revenue Projection Case Study</h2>
                <div class="stats-grid">
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">$3.2M</div>
                        <p>Projected annual revenue from comprehensive representation of a major comedy estate</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">250%</div>
                        <p>Average increase in catalog value after successful digital recreation project</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">15+</div>
                        <p>New revenue streams available through comprehensive legacy management</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-card">
                        <div class="stat-number">$45M</div>
                        <p>Total addressable market for comedy legacy representation by 2025</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card materials">
                <h2>Available Resources</h2>
                <div class="materials-grid">
                    <a href={`${base}estate-model`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Estate Agreement Model</h3>
                            <p>Template contracts and negotiation frameworks</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}revenue-projection`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Revenue Projections</h3>
                            <p>Detailed financial models for estate representation</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}tech-partners`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Technology Partners</h3>
                            <p>Vetted partners for digital recreation implementation</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                    <a href={`${base}legal-framework`} class="material-link">
                        <div class="material-card">
                            <h3>Legal Framework</h3>
                            <p>Comprehensive rights management approach</p>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card contact">
                <h2>Develop Your Estate Representation Strategy</h2>
                <p>Schedule a confidential consultation to explore how your agency can lead in this emerging representation category.</p>
                <a href="mailto:contact@example.com" class="contact-btn">Request Agency Consultation</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    main {
        color: white;
    }

    .hero {
        background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('/living-with-the-ghost-of-sam/images/SamImage.jpg') no-repeat center center;
        background-size: cover;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .subtitle {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        opacity: 0.9;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .content {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
    }

    .info-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .info-card h2 {
        color: #FFD700;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .info-card h3 {
        color: #FFD700;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .info-card ul {
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .info-card li {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .highlight-box {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .highlight-box h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .two-column {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .estate-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .estate-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .estate-card h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    .stats-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .stat-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        text-align: center;
        height: 100%;
    }

    .stat-number {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #FFD700;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .materials-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .material-link {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
    }

    .material-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        transition: transform 0.2s, background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .material-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .contact {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .contact-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #2196F3;
        color: white;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .contact-btn:hover {
        background: #1976D2;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .two-column, .estate-grid, .stats-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .materials-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>
